{"tid":2312733,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"IZ*ONE 回歸倒數兩天！新歌〈Panorama〉舞蹈挑戰提前開跑","createTime":"2020-12-05T08:07:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-05T09:13:36.000Z","uid":16659,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"0618494e2d0e41f8b323b69a59bfde2da5e8c7f3","tid":2312733,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T08:07:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/800_86400_5eaf7c7fa30ac36b69d10e4fd61c0d05/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-12-05/132113-887725.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F800_86400_5eaf7c7fa30ac36b69d10e4fd61c0d05%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-12-05%2F132113-887725.png&h=4869971c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n這週末結束後，IZ*ONE 就會帶著迷你四輯〈One-reeler / Act IV〉回歸，WIZ*ONE 們應該都等不及了吧？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n隨著專輯即將發行，Off the Record 今天（5 日）公開了 IZ*ONE 第四張迷你專輯〈One-reeler / Act IV〉主打歌 &ldquo;Panorama&rdquo; 的第二波 MV 預告片。<br />\n<br />\n有別於主要營造氣氛的首波預告片，新預告在濃豔的色彩襯托下，12 位成員的特寫、華麗的群舞畫面搭配著輕快旋律交錯出現，在延續 IZ*ONE 特有風格的同時，也呼應新專輯概念帶來令人耳目一新的效果。<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_74576b9f9ca5aee2edfb6d8d16b4c23f/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-12-05/132113-887726.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_74576b9f9ca5aee2edfb6d8d16b4c23f%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-12-05%2F132113-887726.jpeg&h=bf157e2b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nIZ*ONE 昨天已搶先在 TikTok 上啟動新歌的舞蹈挑戰活動，而下週一傍晚她們就會帶著〈One-reeler / Act IV〉正式回歸，以 &ldquo;Panorama&rdquo; 為首發表 &ldquo;Mise-en-Sc&egrave;ne&rdquo;、&ldquo;Island&rdquo;、&ldquo;Sequence&rdquo;⋯⋯等六首歌！"},{"pid":"4e78c94149fedee5a078f4dfeb425e421a8f7c64","tid":2312733,"uid":229026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T08:08:15.000Z","msg":"勁巧天<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" 